---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" data-lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="description" content="Tang Yang — Data Analyst. Indicator frameworks, BI dashboards, attribution analysis, consumer insights." />
    <title>Tang Yang — Data Analyst</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Newsreader:ital,opsz,wght@0,6..72,300;0,6..72,400;0,6..72,500;1,6..72,300;1,6..72,400&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@300;400;500&family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>

  <body class="antialiased">

    <!-- ============ HEADER ============ -->
    <header id="hdr" class="fixed inset-x-0 top-0 z-40 transition-all duration-300 border-b border-transparent">
      <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[1280px] px-6 md:px-10 lg:px-14 flex h-16 items-center justify-between">
        <a href="#top" class="group flex items-baseline gap-3">
          <span class="font-display text-[19px] tracking-tight"
                data-i18n data-en="Tang Yang" data-zh="汤洋">Tang Yang</span>
          <span class="hidden sm:inline font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-muted group-hover:text-ink transition"
                data-i18n data-en="Data Analyst" data-zh="数据分析师">Data Analyst</span>
        </a>

        <nav class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-9 font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink2">
          <a class="arrow-link" href="#about"   data-i18n data-en="About"   data-zh="关于">About</a>
          <a class="arrow-link" href="#work"    data-i18n data-en="Work"    data-zh="作品">Work</a>
          <a class="arrow-link" href="#contact" data-i18n data-en="Contact" data-zh="联系">Contact</a>
        </nav>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-1 font-mono text-[12px] tracking-[0.14em]">
          <button id="lang-en" class="px-2 py-1 rounded-sm transition text-ink" aria-pressed="true">EN</button>
          <span class="text-rule">/</span>
          <button id="lang-zh" class="px-2 py-1 rounded-sm transition text-muted hover:text-ink" aria-pressed="false">CN</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
      <section id="top" class="relative pt-32 md:pt-40 pb-20 md:pb-28 grain">
        <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[1280px] px-6 md:px-10 lg:px-14">

          <div class="flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-muted">
            <span data-i18n data-en="Portfolio" data-zh="作品集">Portfolio</span>
            <span>N 31.2° / E 121.4°</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-3 h-px w-full bg-rule"></div>

          <div class="mt-10 md:mt-14 grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 gap-y-12 items-start">

            <!-- Left: kicker + H1 -->
            <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8">
              <div class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-accent mb-6"
                   data-i18n
                   data-en="Data Analyst · Metrics · BI · Insights"
                   data-zh="数据分析师 · 指标 · BI · 洞察">
                Data Analyst · Metrics · BI · Insights
              </div>

              <h1 class="font-display text-[14vw] sm:text-[12vw] md:text-[9.5vw] lg:text-[8.2vw] leading-[0.92] tracking-[-0.025em] text-ink">
                <span class="block" data-i18n data-en="Numbers narrate." data-zh="数字会说话。">Numbers narrate.</span>
                <span class="block italic font-light text-ink2"
                      data-i18n data-en="I write the sentences." data-zh="我把它讲清楚。">I write the sentences.</span>
              </h1>
            </div>

            <!-- Right: analyst card -->
            <aside class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-4 lg:pt-2">
              <div class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-muted"
                   data-i18n data-en="— The analyst" data-zh="— 分析师">— The analyst</div>

              <div class="mt-4 font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight"
                   data-i18n data-en="Tang Yang" data-zh="汤洋">Tang Yang</div>

              <p class="mt-5 max-w-sm text-[15px] leading-[1.65] text-ink2"
                 data-i18n
                 data-en="Three years in. Indicator frameworks, quantitative modeling, attribution and anomaly analysis, BI dashboards."
                 data-zh="数据分析 3 年。指标体系、量化测算、归因分析、异动分析、BI 看板。">
                Three years in. Indicator frameworks, quantitative modeling, attribution and anomaly analysis, BI dashboards.
              </p>

              <div class="mt-6 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-muted"
                   data-i18n data-en="Based in Shanghai" data-zh="常驻上海">Based in Shanghai</div>
            </aside>
          </div>

          <!-- CTAs -->
          <div class="mt-14 md:mt-20 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch sm:items-center gap-3">
            <a href="/Tang_Yang_Data_Analyst.pdf"
               class="group inline-flex items-center justify-between gap-6 bg-ink text-paper px-6 py-4 hover:bg-accent transition-colors"
               download>
              <span class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em]"
                    data-i18n data-en="Download résumé" data-zh="下载简历">Download résumé</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[14px] transition-transform group-hover:translate-y-0.5">↓</span>
            </a>
            <a href="#contact"
               class="group inline-flex items-center justify-between gap-6 border border-ink/80 px-6 py-4 hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper transition-colors">
              <span class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em]"
                    data-i18n data-en="Get in touch" data-zh="联系我">Get in touch</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[14px] transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- ============ ABOUT ============ -->
      <section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-32 border-t border-rule">
        <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[1280px] px-6 md:px-10 lg:px-14">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 gap-y-10">

            <!-- Left: section label + portrait byline -->
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-3">
              <div class="font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-muted"
                   data-i18n data-en="01 — About" data-zh="01 — 关于">01 — About</div>

              <figure class="portrait mt-6 max-w-[240px]">
                <div class="aspect-[3/4] w-full overflow-hidden border border-rule bg-paper2">
                  <img src="/portrait.jpg" alt="Tang Yang portrait" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                </div>
                <figcaption class="mt-3 flex items-center justify-between gap-3 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-muted">
                  <span class="whitespace-nowrap" data-i18n data-en="Fig. — Portrait" data-zh="图 — 肖像">Fig. — Portrait</span>
                  <span class="whitespace-nowrap">2026</span>
                </figcaption>
              </figure>
            </div>

            <!-- Right: heading + dek + mini stats + byline meta -->
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-9 flex flex-col">
              <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.1] tracking-tight max-w-3xl text-ink"
                  data-i18n
                  data-en="A short note from the analyst."
                  data-zh="分析师的一段自述。">A short note from the analyst.</h2>

              <p class="mt-8 font-display italic font-light text-xl md:text-[26px] leading-[1.35] tracking-[-0.005em] text-ink2 max-w-[40ch]"
                 data-i18n
                 data-en="Indicators tell you what changed. Methodology tells you why."
                 data-zh="指标告诉你发生了什么,方法论告诉你为什么。">
                Indicators tell you what changed. Methodology tells you why.
              </p>

              <div class="mt-auto pt-16">
                <div class="h-px w-full bg-rule"></div>
                <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-3 gap-x-6 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em]">
                  <div>
                    <div class="text-muted" data-i18n data-en="By" data-zh="作者">By</div>
                    <div class="mt-1 text-ink" data-i18n data-en="Tang Yang" data-zh="汤洋">Tang Yang</div>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <div class="text-muted" data-i18n data-en="From" data-zh="地点">From</div>
                    <div class="mt-1 text-ink" data-i18n data-en="Shanghai, CN" data-zh="中国 上海">Shanghai, CN</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="text-right">
                    <div class="text-muted" data-i18n data-en="Practicing since" data-zh="入行年份">Practicing since</div>
                    <div class="mt-1 text-ink">2022</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-12 mb-12 h-px w-full bg-rule"></div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 gap-y-12">

            <!-- Bio + Questions -->
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-7">
              <div class="space-y-5 text-[16px] md:text-[17px] leading-[1.7] text-ink2">
                <p class="text-pretty" data-i18n
                   data-en="I'm a data analyst with three years of experience. My day-to-day work includes designing indicator frameworks, quantitative modeling, attribution and anomaly analysis, and building BI dashboards in Tableau, PowerBI, and FineBI. I've delivered across e-commerce, smart manufacturing, finance, and education."
                   data-zh="数据分析师 · 3 年经验。日常工作包括指标体系搭建、量化测算、归因分析、异动分析,以及 Tableau / PowerBI / FineBI 的 BI 看板搭建。服务过电商、智能制造、金融、教育等多种业务场景。">
                  I'm a data analyst with three years of experience. My day-to-day work includes designing indicator frameworks, quantitative modeling, attribution and anomaly analysis, and building BI dashboards in Tableau, PowerBI, and FineBI. I've delivered across e-commerce, smart manufacturing, finance, and education.
                </p>
                <p class="text-pretty" data-i18n
                   data-en="I write before I chart. One clear sentence beats ten clever visuals."
                   data-zh="动笔之前先想清楚结论。一句干净的话,胜过十张花哨的图。">
                  I write before I chart. One clear sentence beats ten clever visuals.
                </p>
              </div>

            </div>

            <!-- Skills + Methods -->
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-5 md:pl-6 md:border-l border-rule space-y-8">
              <div>
                <div class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-muted mb-3"
                     data-i18n data-en="Tools" data-zh="工具">Tools</div>
                <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <li class="font-mono text-[12px] px-2.5 py-1.5 border border-rule text-ink hover:border-ink hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper transition-colors cursor-default">SQL</li>
                  <li class="font-mono text-[12px] px-2.5 py-1.5 border border-rule text-ink hover:border-ink hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper transition-colors cursor-default">Python</li>
                  <li class="font-mono text-[12px] px-2.5 py-1.5 border border-rule text-ink hover:border-ink hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper transition-colors cursor-default">Tableau</li>
                  <li class="font-mono text-[12px] px-2.5 py-1.5 border border-rule text-ink hover:border-ink hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper transition-colors cursor-default">Power BI</li>
                  <li class="font-mono text-[12px] px-2.5 py-1.5 border border-rule text-ink hover:border-ink hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper transition-colors cursor-default">FineBI</li>
                  <li class="font-mono text-[12px] px-2.5 py-1.5 border border-rule text-ink hover:border-ink hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper transition-colors cursor-default">Excel (VBA)</li>
                  <li class="font-mono text-[12px] px-2.5 py-1.5 border border-rule text-ink hover:border-ink hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper transition-colors cursor-default">YingDao RPA</li>
                  <li class="font-mono text-[12px] px-2.5 py-1.5 border border-rule text-ink hover:border-ink hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper transition-colors cursor-default">ChatGPT / Claude</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div>
                <div class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-muted mb-3"
                     data-i18n data-en="Methods" data-zh="方法论">Methods</div>
                <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <li class="font-mono text-[12px] px-2.5 py-1.5 border border-rule text-ink hover:border-ink hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper transition-colors cursor-default"
                      data-i18n data-en="Market Research" data-zh="市场研究">Market Research</li>
                  <li class="font-mono text-[12px] px-2.5 py-1.5 border border-rule text-ink hover:border-ink hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper transition-colors cursor-default"
                      data-i18n data-en="Consumer Insights" data-zh="消费者洞察">Consumer Insights</li>
                  <li class="font-mono text-[12px] px-2.5 py-1.5 border border-rule text-ink hover:border-ink hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper transition-colors cursor-default"
                      data-i18n data-en="KPI Framework" data-zh="指标体系">KPI Framework</li>
                  <li class="font-mono text-[12px] px-2.5 py-1.5 border border-rule text-ink hover:border-ink hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper transition-colors cursor-default"
                      data-i18n data-en="Attribution Analysis" data-zh="归因分析">Attribution Analysis</li>
                  <li class="font-mono text-[12px] px-2.5 py-1.5 border border-rule text-ink hover:border-ink hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper transition-colors cursor-default"
                      data-i18n data-en="Anomaly Analysis" data-zh="异动分析">Anomaly Analysis</li>
                  <li class="font-mono text-[12px] px-2.5 py-1.5 border border-rule text-ink hover:border-ink hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper transition-colors cursor-default"
                      data-i18n data-en="Quantitative Modeling" data-zh="量化测算">Quantitative Modeling</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Timeline -->
          <div class="mt-16 mb-6 h-px w-full bg-rule"></div>
          <div class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em]">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 py-3 border-b border-rule/60">
              <div class="col-span-6 md:col-span-3 text-muted">2024 — 2025</div>
              <div class="col-span-6 md:col-span-3 text-ink"
                   data-i18n data-en="Tianlan Technology" data-zh="天蓝色科技">Tianlan Technology</div>
              <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4 mt-2 md:mt-0 text-ink2"
                   data-i18n data-en="FMCG e-commerce · Data Analyst" data-zh="快消电商 · 数据分析师">FMCG e-commerce · Data Analyst</div>
              <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-2 mt-1 md:mt-0 md:text-right text-muted"
                   data-i18n data-en="Shanghai" data-zh="上海">Shanghai</div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 py-3 border-b border-rule/60">
              <div class="col-span-6 md:col-span-3 text-muted">2022 — 2024</div>
              <div class="col-span-6 md:col-span-3 text-ink">Huawei</div>
              <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4 mt-2 md:mt-0 text-ink2"
                   data-i18n data-en="Smart manufacturing · Data Analyst" data-zh="智能制造 · 数据分析师">Smart manufacturing · Data Analyst</div>
              <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-2 mt-1 md:mt-0 md:text-right text-muted"
                   data-i18n data-en="Shanghai" data-zh="上海">Shanghai</div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 py-3">
              <div class="col-span-6 md:col-span-3 text-muted">2016 — 2022</div>
              <div class="col-span-6 md:col-span-3 text-ink"
                   data-i18n data-en="Yangtze University" data-zh="长江大学">Yangtze University</div>
              <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4 mt-2 md:mt-0 text-ink2"
                   data-i18n data-en="B.E. Communications Engineering" data-zh="通信工程学士">B.E. Communications Engineering</div>
              <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-2 mt-1 md:mt-0 md:text-right text-muted"
                   data-i18n data-en="Education" data-zh="教育背景">Education</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Languages + Industries footnote -->
          <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 gap-y-3 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-muted">
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-3"
                 data-i18n data-en="Languages" data-zh="语言">Languages</div>
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-9 text-ink2"
                 data-i18n data-en="Mandarin (native) · English CET-6"
                 data-zh="普通话(母语) · 英语 CET-6">Mandarin (native) · English CET-6</div>
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-3"
                 data-i18n data-en="Industries" data-zh="行业">Industries</div>
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-9 text-ink2"
                 data-i18n
                 data-en="E-commerce · Smart manufacturing · Finance · Education"
                 data-zh="电商 · 智能制造 · 金融 · 教育">E-commerce · Smart manufacturing · Finance · Education</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- ============ WORK ============ -->
      <section id="work" class="py-24 md:py-32 border-t border-rule">
        <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[1280px] px-6 md:px-10 lg:px-14">

          <!-- Section header -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 gap-y-10">
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-3">
              <div class="font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-muted"
                   data-i18n data-en="02 — Selected work" data-zh="02 — 精选作品">02 — Selected work</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-9">
              <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.05] tracking-tight max-w-3xl text-ink"
                  data-i18n data-en="Selected work." data-zh="精选作品。">Selected work.</h2>
              <p class="mt-6 font-display italic font-light text-xl md:text-[24px] leading-[1.4] text-ink2 max-w-[44ch]"
                 data-i18n
                 data-en="Five rooms. Different problems, same craft — ask the right question, then show the work."
                 data-zh="五个场景。不同的问题,同一份手艺——先问对问题,再把过程展示出来。">
                Five rooms. Different problems, same craft — ask the right question, then show the work.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-14 h-px w-full bg-rule"></div>

          <!-- ============================================== -->
          <!-- 01 · LEAD STORY  — full-bleed landscape image    -->
          <!-- ============================================== -->
          <article class="py-16 md:py-24 border-b border-rule">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 gap-y-6 items-end">
              <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-2">
                <div class="font-display text-[64px] md:text-[88px] leading-[0.85] text-accent">01</div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4">
                <div class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-muted"
                     data-i18n data-en="Reporting automation" data-zh="报表自动化">Reporting automation</div>
                <div class="mt-1 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.05em] text-ink2"
                     data-i18n data-en="Internet finance · Weekly cadence" data-zh="互联网金融 · 周度周期">Internet finance · Weekly cadence</div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6">
                <h3 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-[44px] lg:text-[52px] leading-[1.02] tracking-tight text-ink"
                    data-i18n
                    data-en="Weekly report, automated."
                    data-zh="周报，全自动。">Weekly report, automated.</h3>
              </div>
            </div>

            <figure class="mt-10 md:mt-14">
              <div class="w-full overflow-hidden border border-rule bg-paper2">
                <img src="/work/excel-finance-weekly.png"
                     alt="Excel weekly operations report — internet finance business"
                     class="w-full h-auto block" loading="lazy" />
              </div>
              <figcaption class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-muted">
                <span data-i18n data-en="Fig. 01 — Weekly report dashboard" data-zh="图 01 — 周报看板">Fig. 01 — Weekly report dashboard</span>
                <span>Excel · 2020</span>
              </figcaption>
            </figure>

            <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 gap-y-10">
              <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-7 space-y-5 text-[16px] md:text-[17px] leading-[1.7] text-ink2">
                <p class="text-pretty" data-i18n
                   data-en="An internet finance business needed a standardized weekly operations report. Before this, business teams stitched it by hand every Monday — slow and error-prone. I designed and built the template end-to-end: Excel advanced functions (SUMIFS, INDEX-MATCH, OFFSET) paired with conditional formatting. Change the date, region, or field name and the whole report refreshes itself, with anomalies highlighted automatically across the core operational dimensions — profit, traffic, cost."
                   data-zh="一家互联网金融公司需要一套标准化的周度运营报告。之前业务团队每周一手工拼接,既慢又易错。我从零搭建了报表模板:Excel 进阶函数(SUMIFS、INDEX-MATCH、OFFSET)配合条件格式。修改日期、地区或字段名,整张报表自动刷新,核心运营维度——利润、流量、成本——的异动自动高亮。">
                  An internet finance business needed a standardized weekly operations report. Before this, business teams stitched it by hand every Monday — slow and error-prone. I designed and built the template end-to-end: Excel advanced functions (SUMIFS, INDEX-MATCH, OFFSET) paired with conditional formatting. Change the date, region, or field name and the whole report refreshes itself, with anomalies highlighted automatically across the core operational dimensions — profit, traffic, cost.
                </p>
                <p class="text-pretty" data-i18n
                   data-en="What used to be a 3-hour Monday ritual became minutes of self-service. Metric definitions stay unified across weeks; week-over-week comparison is immediate."
                   data-zh="原本每周一 3 小时的人工拼报,变成了分钟级的自助查询。指标口径周与周之间统一;同比环比即点即得。">
                  What used to be a 3-hour Monday ritual became minutes of self-service. Metric definitions stay unified across weeks; week-over-week comparison is immediate.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-5 md:pl-8 md:border-l border-rule">
                <dl class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-6">
                  <div>
                    <dt class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-muted"
                        data-i18n data-en="Turnaround" data-zh="报表耗时">Turnaround</dt>
